HEADWORD: Distiller
<hw>Dis*till"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who distills; esp., one who extracts alcoholic liquors by
distillation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The condenser of a distilling apparatus.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Distillery</ent>⟦br⟧
